            <p>&#91;Hebrew&#93;<lb/>
                &#34;Jerusalem&#44; &#40;Holy City&#41; the Glory of all Lands.&#34;<lb/>
                ALFRED A. MARCUS &#38; SON&#44;<lb/>
                Diamond Merchants &#38; Importers&#44;<lb/>
                Purchasers of Real Estate &#40;Landed Property&#41;<lb/>
                RESIDENCE&#44; 127 DARTMOUTH ST.&#44; HARD&#45;BY&#45;THE&#45;BRIDGE.<lb/></p>
            <p>No business will be transacted or interviews had on the Jewish Sab&#45;<lb/>bath from one hour before sunset on Friday until one hour after sunset<lb/> on Saturday&#44; or on the Jewish Festivals&#44; and no letters will be opened<lb/> on those days.<lb/></p>
            <p>TELEPHONE &#34;TREMONT&#44;&#34; 457.<lb/>
                Boston&#44; Decr 20 A. M. 5652<lb/></p>
            <p>My very dear Doctor<lb/></p>
            <p>We all are extremely<lb/> anxious to hear from you<lb/> regarding your health which<lb/> we sincerely pray to God<lb/> you are well again kindly<lb/> let us know.  My daughter<lb/> son &#38; myself all join<lb/> Yours most faithfully<lb/> &#38; sincerely<lb/> Alfred A Marcus Jr<lb/></p>
